external_knowledge:
- "ocean of social media posts" represents the large volume of social media data;
- "sailed the stormy waters of public opinion" metaphorically describes experiencing the fluctuating public sentiment reflected in the data;
- "overall sentiment score" refers to the average score calculated from the sum of positive, negative, and neutral sentiment percentages.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT T1.name
FROM cryptocurrencies AS T1
JOIN predictions AS T2 ON T1.crypto_id = T2.crypto_id;

external_knowledge:
- Shining stars of the cryptocurrency universe = Top 10 cryptocurrencies by market capitalization;
- Positive vibes from social media = Percentage of positive sentiment;
- Sparkle in the financial sky = Market capitalization.

sql:
SELECT name, symbol 
FROM cryptocurrencies 
WHERE market_cap > (SELECT AVG(market_cap) FROM cryptocurrencies);
